WEBVTT

00:06:29.429 --> 00:06:32.262
Or is man a wolf for man?

00:06:32.262 --> 00:06:35.150
But this guy doesn't seem too bad.

00:06:35.150 --> 00:06:38.073
He's one of my friends in Tibet.

00:06:38.073 --> 00:06:40.312
He's very kind.

00:06:40.312 --> 00:06:43.937
So now, we love cooperation.

00:06:43.937 --> 00:06:48.275
There's no better joy 
than working together, is there?

00:06:48.275 --> 00:06:52.350
And then not only humans.

00:06:52.350 --> 00:06:54.837
Then, of course, there's
the struggle for life,

00:06:54.837 --> 00:06:59.178
the survival of the fittest,
social Darwinism.

00:06:59.178 --> 00:07:05.015
But in evolution, cooperation --
though competition exists, of course --